Eigental (1890) hanno agevolato l'accesso alla localit\u00e0. Fino al 1845 H. fece parte del territorio com. della citt\u00e0 di Lucerna."]], "wiki_links": [{"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q18029373", "itemLabel": "Hergiswald", "dhsid": "007524", "namefr": "Hergiswald", "articlefr": "https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hergiswald", "namede": "Wallfahrtskirche Hergiswald (Kriens)", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wallfahrtskirche_Hergiswald_(Kriens)", "nameit": "", "articleit": "", "nameen": "", "articleen": "", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q16970", "instanceofLabel": "\u00e9glise", "gndid": "4462506-6"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q18029373", "wikipedia_page_title": null, "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": "H", "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/it/articles/007524/2007-12-11"}